    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Amazon does not do it but they do not have instant search. Google is a bit different since it's not an e-commerce\n\nI think it's good for e-commerce website and it goes with what we pitch which is going back and forth between search and navigation.\nProbably this is not something to put by default. But I think we should be able to do it easily\n",
